OL,3,CHow can I get a refund or compensation
OL,4,Cfor train delays?
OL,6,FTrain services across the UK on Friday
OL,7,Fare facing cancellations or delays of
OL,8,Fup to 15 minutes due to a nationwide
OL,9,Ffault with the radio system used for
OL,10,Fcommunication between train drivers
OL,11,Fand signallers.
OL,13,FDisrupted passengers may be entitled
OL,14,Fto a full refund from the ticket
OL,15,Fretailer or compensation from the
OL,16,Ftrain company responsible for the
OL,17,Fdelay.
OL,19,FBut how can you claim a refund or
OL,20,Fcompensation? ITV News explains.
