OL,3,CHow can I get a refund or compensation
OL,4,Cfor train delays?
OL,6,FCan I get a refund for my train ticket
OL,7,Fand how do I claim it?
OL,9,FYes, if your train is delayed or
OL,10,Fcancelled and you decide not to
OL,11,Ftravel, you can get a full refund for
OL,12,Fyour unused ticket at no extra cost.
OL,14,FIf you want to get a refund for
OL,15,Fanother reason, you may have to pay a
OL,16,Ffee.
OL,18,FContact the retailer where you bought
OL,19,Fthe ticket for a refund.
