OL,3,CHow can I get a refund or compensation
OL,4,Cfor train delays?
OL,6,FIf it was purchased directly from a
OL,7,Ftrain company, reach out to them for
OL,8,Fassistance. You can find their contact
OL,9,Finformation here.
OL,11,FFor tickets bought from self-service
OL,12,Fmachines, check the machine or station
OL,13,Ffor refund instructions.
OL,15,FAm I entitled to compensation, and how
OL,16,Fdo I claim it?
OL,18,FIf your train is delayed or cancelled
OL,19,Fand you arrive late at your
OL,20,Fdestination, you may be entitled to
OL,21,Fcompensation.
