OL,3,CHow can I get a refund or compensation
OL,4,Cfor train delays?
OL,6,FTo claim, you must contact the train
OL,7,Fcompany you travelled with, as
OL,8,Fcompensation schemes vary by operator.
OL,10,FCheck the train company's website for
OL,11,Fspecific details and claim
OL,12,Finstructions.
OL,14,FThe amount you receive depends on:
OL,16,FWhat is Delay Repay?
OL,18,FDelay Repay is a nationwide scheme
OL,19,Fthat lets you claim compensation for
OL,20,Fdelayed train journeys on
OL,21,Fparticipating National Rail services.
